    "description": "Currently, you can boot two instances with the same name... But there are CLI actions that depends on instance name, and you may have unexpected behaviors when using a shared name. See the example:\n\nWe're using essex 2012.1 on CentOS 6.2.\n\n$ nova boot admin03 --flavor m1.small --image bc14a1f5-567c-4ac1-8fab-a65b495a2b17\n(...)\n$ nova boot admin03 --flavor m1.small --image bc14a1f5-567c-4ac1-8fab-a65b495a2b17\n(...)\n\n$ nova list\n+--------------------------------------+-----------+--------+------------------------------------+\n|                  ID                  |    Name   | Status |              Networks              |\n+--------------------------------------+-----------+--------+------------------------------------+\n| 0686b2f8-0995-4460-b21e-c4edbcf3f932 | admin03   | ACTIVE | private_0=172.25.8.16, 10.170.1.19 |\n| 330cbcc3-4899-47a2-8b34-ce6f01b5bb70 | new       | ACTIVE | private_0=172.25.8.17              |\n| 4e607d9c-0536-454c-ade7-ae2e8c921803 | admin02   | ACTIVE | private_0=172.25.8.14, 10.170.1.17 |\n| 83449c48-a025-44c3-bad3-deee46017309 | admin03   | ACTIVE | private_0=172.25.8.13              |\n| 9be68852-bb24-41ea-9d5d-908b33466af4 | admin01   | ACTIVE | private_0=172.25.8.10, 10.170.1.12 |\n| bf5b4403-8419-4249-96ab-5dc7cf78b3ed | Server 37 | ACTIVE | private_0=172.25.8.11, 10.170.1.16 |\n+--------------------------------------+-----------+--------+------------------------------------+\n\nAs you can see, there are two instances with admin03 name. Now, if I delete using the admin03 name, I'm not able to tell which of the machines are going to be deleted:\n\n$ nova delete admin03\n+--------------------------------------+-----------+--------+------------------------------------+\n|                  ID                  |    Name   | Status |              Networks              |\n+--------------------------------------+-----------+--------+------------------------------------+\n| 0686b2f8-0995-4460-b21e-c4edbcf3f932 | admin03   | ACTIVE | private_0=172.25.8.16, 10.170.1.19 |\n| 330cbcc3-4899-47a2-8b34-ce6f01b5bb70 | new       | ACTIVE | private_0=172.25.8.17, 10.170.1.21 |\n| 4e607d9c-0536-454c-ade7-ae2e8c921803 | admin02   | ACTIVE | private_0=172.25.8.14, 10.170.1.17 |\n| 9be68852-bb24-41ea-9d5d-908b33466af4 | admin01   | ACTIVE | private_0=172.25.8.10, 10.170.1.12 |\n| bf5b4403-8419-4249-96ab-5dc7cf78b3ed | Server 37 | ACTIVE | private_0=172.25.8.11, 10.170.1.16 |\n+--------------------------------------+-----------+--------+------------------------------------+", 
